<!-- linxira-skills:start -->
## Linxira Skills

Project-local Linxira content is materialized as a progressive routing tree under
`.agents/skills/`. Read only one matching top-level router first:

{{routes}}

Follow that router to one second-level index, then load the primary leaf skill
required by the task. Load an additional leaf only when the primary skill names
it as a dependency or an independent risk gate requires a companion contract.
Do not scan or preload the complete tree, and do not combine overlapping
alternatives. Follow every selected leaf's risk and completion requirements
before action.
<!-- linxira-skills:end -->
